title: Spyder Auto Installation: 2007-2012 Honda CR-V Step Bars
description: This video will guide you through the installation process for a set of step bars, applicable for 2007 through 2012 Honda CR-V crossovers. By following along with this video you should be able to install a set of step bars on your own vehicle.
